; ── VN direction markers (lore/_VN_DIRECTION_PLAYBOOK.md) ──
; shot_* Marker3D = camera framing (group "vn_shot", metadata/fov).
; cast_* Marker3D = character blocking anchors at FLOOR level for
; the [stage:<char> <spot>] directive — the marker's yaw is the
; direction the staged model faces. Coordinates derived from
; build_diner.py geometry (Blender→Godot: gx=bx, gy=bz, gz=-by).

